overview: It's chilly outside, and there's nothing Cali enjoys more than warming up beside a roaring fireplace. Things heat up as Cali strips down - she just can't help but take a little time to indulge herself. Valentina is a rare pearl, so why not treat her like one? After lounging in a luxurious bath filled to the brim with pearls and oil, Valentina treats us to a tasty tease of her bountiful booty. When it comes to sex, aggressive Adriana isn’t afraid to get a little messy - she’s not satisfied until she’s drenched with sweat, spit and spunk. Lifelong safari enthusiast Mick Blue has seen a whole lot over the years. Nothing comes close to spotting the elusive Kat Dior in her natural habitat. Cathy gets ready for a dreamy night of self-care, prepping a bath with rose petals and pouring oil on herself and into the bath.
title: Wet & Wild Asses 4
